      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a masterclass in high-revving atmospheric induction: a collector-grade E92 M3. This specimen features the legendary S65 4.0L V8, delivering linear power delivery up to an 8,400 RPM redline through eight individual throttle bodies. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission provides lightning-fast gear synchronization, paired with the M Variable Differential Lock for optimal lateral traction. Chassis rigidity remains factory-spec, complemented by the weight-saving carbon fiber roof panel for a lowered center of gravity. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history ensuring rod bearing integrity and VANOS health. The finish exhibits original factory depth, and the interior retains its showroom-fresh tactile feedback. A mechanically pure example for the discerning enthusiast.",
