      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, museum-quality example that defies its age. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, presenting in a state that mirrors its original delivery day. The exterior finish retains a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections, further protected by a professionally applied multi-layer ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of bolster wear, the original factory scent is preserved, and every piece of brushed aluminum and wood trim is free of micro-scratches. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been serviced exclusively at certified intervals with a complete binder of records included. It sits on a fresh set of high-performance tires and has recently undergone a comprehensive preventative fluid service. This is not just a used car; it is a turnkey collector\u2019s piece for the most discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
